"Picks up pending `lu.ai.llm.request` records and dispatches to the provider"
msgstr ""
"대기 중인 `lu.ai.llm.request` 레코드를 선택하여 공급자로 전달합니다"

#: ../../ai-agent/architecture.md:343
msgid "`ir_cron_workflow_timeout`"
msgstr "`ir_cron_workflow_timeout`"

#: ../../ai-agent/architecture.md:343
msgid "`data/ir_cron_workflow_timeout.xml`"
msgstr "`data/ir_cron_workflow_timeout.xml`"

#: ../../ai-agent/architecture.md:343
msgid ""
"Marks stalled workflow states as `timeout` after the configured threshold"
msgstr ""
"설정된 임계값 이후 지연된 워크플로 상태를 `timeout`으로 표시합니다"

#: ../../ai-agent/architecture.md:345
msgid ""
"This decouples user-facing response latency from heavy multi-step workflows."
msgstr ""
"이는 사용자 대면 응답 지연을 무거운 다단계 워크플로에서 분리합니다."

#: ../../ai-agent/architecture.md:347
msgid "Caching & Connection Pooling"
msgstr "캐싱 & 연결 풀링"

#: ../../ai-agent/architecture.md:349
msgid ""
"- **Embedding vectors** are stored per-chunk in `ai.embedding` and reused "
"across queries.\n"
"- **Prompt templates** are cached in `data/prompt_templates.xml` (loaded by "
"`lu_ai_edge`).\n"
"- The Ollama client maintains persistent HTTP connections; avoid setting a "
"very short `OLLAMA_KEEP_ALIVE` on the server side to benefit from model "
"keep-warm."
msgstr ""
"- **임베딩 벡터**는 청크별로 `ai.embedding`에 저장되고 쿼리 전체에서 재사용됩니다.\n"
"- **프롬프트 템플릿**은 `data/prompt_templates.xml`에 캐시됩니다(`lu_ai_edge`에서 로드).\n"
"- Ollama 클라이언트는 지속적인 HTTP 연결을 유지합니다. "
"모델 keep-warm의 이점을 얻으려면 서버 측에서 매우 짧은 `OLLAMA_KEEP_ALIVE`를 설정하지 마세요."

#: ../../ai-agent/architecture.md:355
msgid "Extending the Architecture"
msgstr "아키텍처 확장"

#: ../../ai-agent/architecture.md:357
msgid "Creating a Custom Domain Agent"
msgstr "커스텀 도메인 에이전트 생성"

#: ../../ai-agent/architecture.md:359
msgid ""
"Domain agents follow the `lu_ai_orch_*` pattern. The minimum required is an "
"XML data file that registers a `lu.ai.orchestrator.route` record:"
msgstr ""
"도메인 에이전트는 `lu_ai_orch_*` 패턴을 따릅니다. "
"필요한 최소 요구사항은 `lu.ai.orchestrator.route` 레코드를 등록하는 XML 데이터 파일입니다:"

#: ../../ai-agent/architecture.md:361
msgid ""
"```xml\n"
"<record id=\"route_my_domain\" model=\"lu.ai.orchestrator.route\">\n"
"    <field name=\"name\">My Domain</field>\n"
"    <field name=\"active\">True</field>\n"
"    <field name=\"system_prompt\">You are an expert in ...</field>\n"
"    <field name=\"model_fields\">field_a,field_b,field_c</field>\n"
"</record>\n"
"```"
msgstr ""
"```xml\n"
"<record id=\"route_my_domain\" model=\"lu.ai.orchestrator.route\">\n"
"    <field name=\"name\">My Domain</field>\n"
"    <field name=\"active\">True</field>\n"
"    <field name=\"system_prompt\">You are an expert in ...</field>\n"
"    <field name=\"model_fields\">field_a,field_b,field_c</field>\n"
"</record>\n"
"```"

#: ../../ai-agent/architecture.md:370
msgid ""
"Add a Python model only if you need to override routing logic or add custom"
" fields. See :doc:`domain-routing` for a complete walkthrough."
msgstr ""
"라우팅 로직을 오버라이드하거나 커스텀 필드를 추가해야 하는 경우에만 Python 모델을 추가합니다. "
"완전한 단계별 설명은 :doc:`domain-routing`을 참고하세요."

#: ../../ai-agent/architecture.md:372
msgid "Adding a Custom Workflow Step Type"
msgstr "커스텀 워크플로 스텝 타입 추가"

#: ../../ai-agent/architecture.md:374
msgid ""
"New step types are registered in `lu.ai.workflow.step` by extending the "
"`step_type` selection field:"
msgstr ""
"새 스텝 타입은 `step_type` 선택 필드를 확장하여 `lu.ai.workflow.step`에 등록됩니다:"

#: ../../ai-agent/architecture.md:376
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"class MyWorkflowStep(models.Model):\n"
"    _inherit = 'lu.ai.workflow.step'\n"
"\n"
"    step_type = fields.Selection(\n"
"        selection_add=[('my_type', 'My Custom Step')],\n"
"    )\n"
"\n"
"    def _execute_my_type(self, state):\n"
"        # Custom execution logic\n"
"        ...\n"
"```"
msgstr ""
"```python\n"
"class MyWorkflowStep(models.Model):\n"
"    _inherit = 'lu.ai.workflow.step'\n"
"\n"
"    step_type = fields.Selection(\n"
"        selection_add=[('my_type', 'My Custom Step')],\n"
"    )\n"
"\n"
"    def _execute_my_type(self, state):\n"
"        # Custom execution logic\n"
"        ...\n"
"```"

#: ../../ai-agent/architecture.md:389
msgid ""
"Register the execution handler in the parent workflow's `_execute_step` "
"dispatch table. See :doc:`workflows` for the step execution API."
msgstr ""
"실행 핸들러를 부모 워크플로의 `_execute_step` 디스패치 테이블에 등록합니다. "
"스텝 실행 API는 :doc:`workflows`를 참고하세요."

#: ../../ai-agent/architecture.md:391
msgid "Enterprise Hook Points via `lu_ai_edge`"
msgstr "`lu_ai_edge`를 통한 엔터프라이즈 훅 포인트"

#: ../../ai-agent/architecture.md:393
msgid "`lu_ai_edge` exposes three main extension points:"
msgstr "`lu_ai_edge`는 세 가지 주요 확장 포인트를 노출합니다:"

#: ../../ai-agent/architecture.md:395
msgid "Extension point"
msgstr "확장 포인트"

#: ../../ai-agent/architecture.md:395
msgid "Model"
msgstr "모델"

#: ../../ai-agent/architecture.md:395
msgid "Override method"
msgstr "오버라이드 메서드"

#: ../../ai-agent/architecture.md:395
msgid "Purpose"
msgstr "목적"

#: ../../ai-agent/architecture.md:397
